{"id":7169,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><FONT face=黑体><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《<FONT face=黑体>炎黄春秋</FONT>》<FONT face=黑体>编辑部</FONT>：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　看了贵刊今年第一期张家康写《毛泽东领导</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动》一文，我们感到纳闷和不解，贵刊为什么要登载这样的文章？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动过去近</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">60</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年了，历史的尘埃早已落定，许多事情现在已看得很清楚，当年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">（打击贪污犯）是被严重扩大化了，而张文却津津乐道打虎的成绩、数字，并大段引述毛泽东关于打虎的指示，以此证明</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的完全</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">正确</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。例如文中称，毛泽东指示：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">无论党政军在哪一系统，哪一机关，只要是大批地管钱管物的，就一定有大批的贪污犯。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">要各地作出打</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">老虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的估计数字，认为每个省、每个城市及大军区单位都有一百只至几百只</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">大老虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，如捉不到，就是打了败仗。随后，毛泽东又发出要各地限期向中央报告打</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">预算和县区乡开展</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动的电报，指出：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">凡至今尚未做出打虎预算的，限于电到三日内做出此项预算，报告中央。并须准备随时自动追加预算，随时报告中央。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">他在批示全国学习华北军区</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">经验时称：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">华北军区过去成绩甚微，经过严词督责，最近五天突飞猛进，捉虎甚多，令人振奋。打虎要有一套战术，凡已普遍展开的，就要迅速总结经验，组织专门打虎部队，向大小老虎突击。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">于是，全国各地大小单位都成立了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">队，掀起了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">高潮。张文还引毛的指示，要各级领导仿照实行惩治反革命条例那样，大张旗鼓地如同镇压反革命一样地开展</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　毛泽东这些指示带有明显的主观随意性，对当时党内出现的贪污腐化现象作了过于严重估计，以致采用镇压反革命份子的方法，大张旗鼓地搞群众运动。就广东（广州）的情况来看，由于毛一再下达强令性的打虎指标，并不断追加指标，致使当地的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动被严重扩大化。据后来复查，当时《南方日报》点名的所谓</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">大老虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，后来查实全都是搞错了的，都给予平反了。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　不断追加</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">指标，还酿造了惊动中央最高领导的王剑朋凶杀案。广州市企业局局长王剑朋是一位老红军，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动中，下属一家公司被查出贪污</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">窝案</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，该公司负责人被隔离审查，在被审讯过程中，诬指王剑朋也参与作案，王剑朋拒不承认贪污，并打死诬告者和看管人员。运动后期查实，无论王剑朋还是诬告者都没有贪污，但杀人偿命，结果王被毛泽东批准处以极刑。此案现虽已平反，但深究激化矛盾的背后原因，不能说与运动被严重扩大化无关。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　张文也承认毛的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">做预算定指标，多少带有一定的主观性</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，但其全文通篇都在肯定</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">打虎</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">扩大化的做法，甚至借毛的话来肯定苏联的肃反，称</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">只有这样党才能健康。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">苏联在二十世纪五十年代已承认其肃反严重扩大化，张文却在二十一世纪的今天还在美化苏联的肃反，不知其用意何在？更有甚者，张文在最后称对</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">无论给以什么样的积极肯定都是不过分的。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">如此说来，岂不是今后还要继续开展</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　大家都知道，解放后历次政治运动几乎没有不错伤自己的同志的，真是运动不断，冤案如山。正是总结了正反两方面的经验教训，邓小平和十一届三中全会宣布摒弃以阶级斗争为纲，今后不再搞政治运动。这是十分英明正确的。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　当前，贪污腐败问题比当年开展</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动时不知严重多少倍，早已到了天怒人怨的地步。如不解决腐败问题，亡党亡国的危险将不是戏言。实践证明，解决问题不能靠运动，要靠法治、靠制度。只有真正建立健全法制，从制度的层面上入手，才能有效遏制腐败、消除腐败。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　因此，我们不同意张家康文章的观点。希贵刊在选登文章时，注意严格把好史实关，引导读者正确总结历史经验教训，发挥历史对今天的借鉴作用。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">（该文所表述的内容为作者本人观点，与《炎黄春秋》杂志及炎黄春秋网的观点和立场无关。）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>","title":"我们不同意张家康文章的观点（读者来信）","time":1270666961000}